# 🛠️ PART 4: “BIR-READY” FEATURE CHECKLIST (FOR YOUR DEV TEAM)

Your system must include:


## 🧾 Receipt Module

- Business details auto-filled
- TIN + VAT breakdown
- Serial control (non-reusable)

***


## 📊 Reporting

- Daily sales summary (Z-reading equivalent)
- VAT reports
- Sales journal export

***


## 🔐 Security

- Role-based login
- Activity logs
- No hard delete

***


## 🧮 Tax Engine

- 12% VAT auto compute
- VAT-exempt toggle
- Senior/PWD discount support (optional but strong feature)

***


## ☁️ Cloud Requirements (if SaaS)

- Per-client database isolation
- Secure backups
- Data retention (10 years)

***


